      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED STILETTO (2) turned in a solid run last start over 600m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (35.32). Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Worth another chance. DENTON (8) is a promising dog in the frame at 12 of 27 starts including seven wins and was in the minors again latest (29.97) over 515m at this track. Goes very well from this box. Will go close here with a clear run. BROOKDENE (4) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (30.10) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. WYNBURN RITA (1) will be thereabouts after strong recent winning form.",
